5*2^{n+2} - 6*2^{n+1} =2*(5*2^{n+1})- (5*2^{n+1}) - 2^{n+1}
2*(5*2^{n+1})- (5*2^{n+1}) - 2^{n+1} =(5*2^{n+1})(2 - 1) - 2^{n+1} = (5*2^{n+1}) - 2^{n+1} 
 (5*2^{n+1}) - 2^{n+1} = 4*2^{n+1} = 2*2^{n+2} = 2^{n+3} 
